AOL's not letting me check my mail, so anyone sending me private 
email please be patient.

::DrillBit::

DrillBit grabbs on to the hands of his chair, looking out of the 
cockpit at the speeding land. He glances at the scanners, noticing a 
Maximal signature nearby.

"There's a Maximal ahead of us," DrillBit says, pointing to the 
scanners.
